{"word":"νοστέω","slug":"νοστέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>νοστέω</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to come</i> or <i>go back, return</i>, <a href='S:especially'>esp.</a> to one's home or country, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to return safe, to escape</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}